N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 93.7 - Prior transactions

State Regulations

Aircraft reinsurance transactions entered into by an authorized life insurer before the effective date of this Part shall be included in the accounting reports and records of such insurer. Insurers shall be subject to this Part as to all transactions, including renewals, entered into on or after the effective date hereof. Notes
